X-API-Key: dev-api-key-12345

###

### Create new user (with valid API key)
POST {{UserManagmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/user
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: dev-api-key-12345

{
    "name": "Alice Wilson",
    "salary": 65000,
    "department": "Marketing"
}

###

### Update existing user (with valid API key)
PUT {{UserManagmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/user/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: dev-api-key-12345

{
    "name": "John Doe Updated",
    "salary": 55000,
    "department": "IT"
}

###

### Delete user (with valid API key)
DELETE {{UserManagmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/user/3
X-API-Key: dev-api-key-12345

